title: $34+ O/W Summer Airfare Sale from JetBlue
text:
Home > Flight Deals > $34+ O/W Summer Airfare Sale from JetBlue $34+ O/W Summer Airfare Sale from JetBlue May 22, 2015 1:59pm by Patricia Magaña , SmarterTravel Staff Tweet 
JetBlue's latest airfare promotion discounts flights during the most popular travel season—summer. Featured destinations include U.S., Caribbean, and Latin American cities. One-way flights are available and start at $34, but if booking round-trip then pricing starts at $68. 
This sale's travel window varies by route and generally falls between May 29 - September 18, and there's no booking deadline, so pricing and route may change at any time. EDITOR'S OVERVIEW Where to Book: We found the best prices for the travel window of these sales by using a flexible date search, which can be accessed through our flight comparison tool to the right.
